node.title: Stood down Air NZ workers showing COVID-19 symptoms - CEO Greg Foran
node.description: Air NZ CEO Greg Foran says some of the stood down Air NZ workers are showing COVID-19 symptoms.
node.content: ["Air NZ CEO Greg Foran says some of the stood down Air NZ workers are showing COVID-19 symptoms.", "He says he expects there to be more COVID cases among those workers confirmed in the coming days", "More to come...", "RNZ"]
